---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Support the Research — Buddy · AIIT-THRESI" description="Help keep AIIT-THRESI research alive. Every dollar goes directly to the work — electricity, compute, patents, corpus.">

<section style="padding-top: 160px; min-height: 80vh;">
  <div class="container narrow" style="max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 8vw;">

    <div class="eyebrow">Keep it alive</div>
    <h1 style="font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 7vw, 5.5rem); margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.1;">Help keep<br>the lights on.</h1>
    <p class="support-sub">
      This is one guy, a 3090, a stack of provisional patents, and 153 papers written in the dark.
      No VC. No institution. No grant. Just the work.
      If any of it has meant something to you — here's how to make it keep going.
    </p>

    <div class="support-tiers">
      <div class="st-label">CHOOSE YOUR TIER</div>
      <div class="st-grid">

        <div class="st-card">
          <div class="st-tier-name">Supporter</div>
          <div class="st-amount">$10 / month</div>
          <div class="st-desc">Keep the lights on. This is the light bill tier. You're directly paying for the electricity that runs the 3090 in Oklahoma.</div>
          <a href="https://buy.stripe.com/14A00l83Ab0t3q2gx7fbq00" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="st-btn">Become a Supporter →</a>
        </div>

        <div class="st-card featured">
          <div class="st-badge">most impactful</div>
          <div class="st-tier-name">Visionary</div>
          <div class="st-amount">$50 / month</div>
          <div class="st-desc">You're funding real compute cycles. GPU runs, patent clock, the corpus growing. You're in the research. When this becomes something — you were there.</div>
          <a href="https://buy.stripe.com/14A00l83Ab0t3q2gx7fbq00" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="st-btn featured-btn">Become a Visionary →</a>
        </div>

        <div class="st-card">
          <div class="st-tier-name">One-Time</div>
          <div class="st-amount">Any amount</div>
          <div class="st-desc">No commitment. Just pay what feels right. Every dollar goes to the work — not overhead, not marketing, not salaries.</div>
          <a href="https://buy.stripe.com/14A00l83Ab0t3q2gx7fbq00" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="st-btn">Contribute →</a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="support-breakdown">
      <div class="sb-label">WHERE IT GOES</div>

      <div class="sb-item urgent">
        <div class="sb-icon">⚡</div>
        <div class="sb-content">
          <div class="sb-name">Electricity <span class="sb-tag urgent-tag">most urgent</span></div>
          <div class="sb-desc">The 3090 that runs Buddy training draws real power. Council Hill, Oklahoma. Real light bill. This one comes first.</div>
          <div class="sb-amount">~$200 / month</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="sb-item">
        <div class="sb-icon">🖥️</div>
        <div class="sb-content">
          <div class="sb-name">GPU Compute</div>
          <div class="sb-desc">RunPod A100 time for training runs. Local 3090 handles inference. Cloud handles the heavy fine-tuning cycles when they need to happen.</div>
          <div class="sb-amount">~$80–200 / run</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="sb-item">
        <div class="sb-icon">☁️</div>
        <div class="sb-content">
          <div class="sb-name">Hosting & Infrastructure</div>
          <div class="sb-desc">Cloudflare Pages, Render (Victim Advocate, AnchorForge), domain registration, KV storage. The site you're on right now.</div>
          <div class="sb-amount">~$50 / month</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="sb-item">
        <div class="sb-icon">📄</div>
        <div class="sb-content">
          <div class="sb-name">Patent Filings</div>
          <div class="sb-desc">4 provisionals filed. Non-provisional clock is running — 12 months from April 2026. USPTO filing fees, attorney review when we get there.</div>
          <div class="sb-amount">$1,600–4,000 / filing</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="sb-item">
        <div class="sb-icon">🔬</div>
        <div class="sb-content">
          <div class="sb-name">Research & Corpus</div>
          <div class="sb-desc">665GB of training data and growing. Storage drives, ingestion bandwidth, annotation time. The corpus is the foundation — everything Buddy becomes starts here.</div>
          <div class="sb-amount">ongoing</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="sb-item future">
        <div class="sb-icon">🤝</div>
        <div class="sb-content">
          <div class="sb-name">Team <span class="sb-tag future-tag">when we get there</span></div>
          <div class="sb-desc">Right now it's one person. When the research is ready to scale, the people who helped make it possible get taken care of first.</div>
          <div class="sb-amount">—</div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="support-honest">
      <div class="sh-label">THE HONEST VERSION</div>
      <p>There's no overhead here. No salaries, no office, no marketing budget. When you support this, you're paying for the literal electricity that keeps a GPU warm in Oklahoma so a coherence framework that took a year to derive can keep being built.</p>
      <p>If the $400K weather patent raise goes through — you'll have been part of why it existed to raise. That's the bet.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="donate-btn-wrap" style="margin-top: 48px;">
      <a href="https://buy.stripe.com/14A00l83Ab0t3q2gx7fbq00" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="donate-btn">
        Support the Research →
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .eyebrow {
    font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
    font-size: 0.72em;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--teal, #40c0b0);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .support-sub {
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 620px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .donate-btn-wrap {
    margin-bottom: 56px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .donate-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--teal, #40c0b0);
    color: #000;
    font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
    font-size: 0.85em;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 14px 32px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: none;
    transition: opacity 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
  }
  .donate-btn:hover { opacity: 0.85; transform: translateY(-1px); border-bottom: none; }

  .donate-note {
    font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
    font-size: 0.7em;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .support-breakdown {
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .sb-label {
    font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
    font-size: 0.68em;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .sb-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    padding: 20px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--edge);
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .sb-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .sb-icon {
    font-size: 1.4em;
    min-width: 32px;
    padding-top: 2px;
  }

  .sb-content { flex: 1; }

  .sb-name {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .sb-tag {
    font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
    font-size: 0.65em;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 3px;
  }
  .urgent-tag { background: rgba(248,113,113,0.12); color: #f87171; border: 1px solid rgba(248,113,113,0.3); }
  .future-tag { background: rgba(147,130,220,0.12); color: var(--violet, #9382dc); border: 1px solid rgba(147,130,220,0.28); }

  .sb-desc {
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .sb-amount {
    font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
    font-size: 0.72em;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--teal, #40c0b0);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .sb-item.urgent .sb-icon { filter: drop-shadow(0 0 6px rgba(248,113,113,0.4)); }
  .sb-item.future { opacity: 0.7; }

  .support-honest {
    background: rgba(64,192,176,0.05);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--teal, #40c0b0);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 24px 28px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .sh-label {
    font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
    font-size: 0.68em;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--teal, #40c0b0);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .support-honest p {
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    font-size: 0.94rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .support-honest p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  /* --- Tiers --- */
  .support-tiers {
    margin-bottom: 52px;
  }

  .st-label {
    font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
    font-size: 0.68em;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .st-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 16px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .st-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  .st-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--edge);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 24px 20px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .st-card.featured {
    border-color: var(--teal, #40c0b0);
    background: rgba(64,192,176,0.04);
  }

  .st-badge {
    font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
    font-size: 0.6em;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--teal, #40c0b0);
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }

  .st-tier-name {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .st-amount {
    font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
    font-size: 0.88em;
    color: var(--teal, #40c0b0);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  .st-desc {
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .st-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 8px;
    font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
    font-size: 0.72em;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--teal, #40c0b0);
    border: 1px solid rgba(64,192,176,0.4);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 9px 16px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s;
  }
  .st-btn:hover { background: rgba(64,192,176,0.1); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(64,192,176,0.4); }

  .featured-btn {
    background: var(--teal, #40c0b0);
    color: #000;
    border-color: var(--teal, #40c0b0);
  }
  .featured-btn:hover { opacity: 0.85; background: var(--teal, #40c0b0); color: #000; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--teal, #40c0b0); }
</style>
